『科學的形上學』國際研討會(韓國首爾, 2010,8/3-5)邀稿


          Submitted on 週三, 11/25/2009 - 18:33        


RELIMINARY CONFERENCE ANNOUNCEMENT The Korean Society for Analytic Philosophy and Metaphysics Research Group at Kyung Hee University (South Korea) will jointly host an international conference on the metaphysics of science from Tuesday 3rd August to Thursday 5th August, 2010. The conference aims to identify and explore fundamental metaphysical issues surrounding science in its broadest sense. The speakers include: Alexander Bird (Bristol Uni. UK) Huw Price (Sydney, Australia) Anjan Chakravartty (Toronto, Canada) Toby Handfield (Monash, Australia) Helen Beebee (Birmingham, UK) Additionally, we may have the following speakers: Lars Bo Gundersen (Aarhus, Denmark) Eline Busck Gundersen (Aarhus, Denmark) Nikolaj Jang Lee Linding Pedersen (UCLA, USA) Philosophers from Korea, Japan, and Taiwan. Further details will be available at http://choise80.khu.ac.kr/ in due course.     研討會臺灣聯絡人： 鄭凱元 中正大學哲學系副教授 kcheng1970@gmail.com   
